<div class="create_form">
  <form action="/signup" class="listing_form" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="signup_listing_form" method="post">
    <div style="margin:0;padding:0;display:inline">
      <input name="authenticity_token" type="hidden" value="AHtnEay+m9HUYtyE/lFp38GEY6A5TqaasIi29NANjGY=" />
    </div>
    <div class="image_upload"> 
      <h2>First, add a picture of your best work</h2> 
      <img align="right" alt="Img_uploadsample" src="/images/img_uploadsample.png" style="margin-left: 10px;" /> 
      <p>Upload an image of your work that best represents your primary style. You can always change this image after your card has been created.</p> 
      <p><strong>For best results upload a 900 x 630 JPG or PNG.</strong><br /> 
      <em>Don&rsquo;t have that size? We&rsquo;ll resize what you have to make sure it fits.</em></p>
      <div id="upload_progress_file"> 
        <input accept="image/*" id="listing_portfolio_images_attributes_0_image" name="listing[portfolio_images_attributes][0][image]" size="30" style="width: 300px; height: 21px;" type="file" /> 
      </div> 
      <div id="upload_progress_bar" style="display:none"> 
        <img alt="Spinner-small" src="/images/spinner-small.gif" />
      </div> 
      <p><label for="listing_portfolio_images_attributes_0_description">Describe the image you just added</label><br /><small>Example: This is a screenshot from our latest homepage redesign of starbucks.com</small><br />
      <textarea cols="40" id="listing_portfolio_images_attributes_0_description" name="listing[portfolio_images_attributes][0][description]" rows="20"></textarea></p> 
    </div>
    <div class="about_company"> 
      <h2>Now, tell us about your business</h2> 
      <p><label for="listing_company_name">What's your company name?</label><br /> 
      <small>You can use your own name if you're a freelancer and don't have a company name.</small></p> 
      <input id="listing_company_name" name="listing[company_name]" size="30" type="text" /> 
      <p><label for="listing_logo">Upload your company logo</label> &ndash; optional<br /> 
      <small>GIF, JPG, or PNG. We&rsquo;ll resize what you have.<br />This is shown on your listing page for clients to see.</small></p> 
      <input accept="image/*" id="listing_logo" name="listing[logo]" size="30" style="width: 300px; height: 21px;" type="file" /> 
      <p><label for="listing_budget_id">What type of budgets do you typically work with?</label></p> 
      <div class="budget_choices"> 
        <label for="listing_budget_id_1"><input id="listing_budget_id_1" name="listing[budget_id]" type="radio" value="1" />&nbsp;<span class='budget_label'>$3,000 and under</span></label> 
      </div> 
      <div class="budget_choices"> 
        <label for="listing_budget_id_2"><input id="listing_budget_id_2" name="listing[budget_id]" type="radio" value="2" />&nbsp;<span class='budget_label'>$3,000-$10,000</span></label> 
      </div> 
      <div class="budget_choices"> 
        <label for="listing_budget_id_3"><input id="listing_budget_id_3" name="listing[budget_id]" type="radio" value="3" />&nbsp;<span class='budget_label'>$10,000-$25,000</span></label> 
      </div> 
      <div class="budget_choices"> 
        <label for="listing_budget_id_4"><input id="listing_budget_id_4" name="listing[budget_id]" type="radio" value="4" />&nbsp;<span class='budget_label'>$25,000-$50,000</span></label> 
      </div> 
      <div class="budget_choices"> 
        <label for="listing_budget_id_5"><input id="listing_budget_id_5" name="listing[budget_id]" type="radio" value="5" />&nbsp;<span class='budget_label'>Over $50,000</span></label> 
      </div> 
      <p> 
        <label for="listing_location_id">Which city or metro area is closest to your company headquarters?</label><br /> 
<small>&bull; If your company has multiple locations, choose the main location.<br />&bull; If your city is not listed, choose &ldquo;My city is not listed&rdquo;.</small> 
      </p> 
      <select id="listing_location_id" name="listing[location_id]"><option value="">Select a location...</option> 
        <option value="464">Atlanta</option> 
        <option value="465">Boston</option> 
        <option value="466">Chicago</option> 
        <option value="14">Washington</option> 
        <option value="0">My city is not listed</option>
      </select> 
      <div id="other_listing_location" style="display: none;"> 
        <div class="us_select"> 
          <div class="us"> 
            <label for="listing_in_us_yes"><input checked="checked" id="listing_in_us_yes" name="listing[in_us]" type="radio" value="yes" />&nbsp;<span class='us'>I'm in the US</span></label> 
          </div> 
          <div class="us"> 
            <label for="listing_in_us_no"><input id="listing_in_us_no" name="listing[in_us]" type="radio" value="no" />&nbsp;<span class='us'>I'm outside of the US</span></label> 
          </div> 
        </div> 
        <div id="other_listing_location_state" style="display: none; clear: both;"> 
          <p>
            <label for="listing_state_id">Select your state</label><br /> 
            <select id="listing_state_id" name="listing[state_id]">
              <option value=""></option> 
              <option value="1">Alabama</option> 
              <option value="2">Alaska</option> 
              <option value="50">Wisconsin</option> 
              <option value="51">Wyoming</option>
            </select>
          </p> 
        </div> 
        <div id="other_listing_location_country" style="display: none; clear: both;"> 
          <p><label for="listing_country_id">Select your country</label><br /> 
            <select id="listing_country_id" name="listing[country_id]"><option value=""></option> 
              <option value="1">Afghanistan</option> 
              <option value="2">Åland Islands</option> 
              <option value="3">Albania</option> 
              <option value="4">Algeria</option> 
              <option value="244">Zambia</option> 
              <option value="245">Zimbabwe</option>
            </select>
          </p> 
        </div> 
        <p><label for="listing_other_location">Enter the city/metro area closest to your headquarters</label><br /> 
          <small>&bull; If your company has multiple locations, just enter the main location.<br />&bull; As you type we'll make recommendations &mdash; please select one if it's close.<br /></small> 
        </p> 
        <input autocomplete="off" id="listing_other_location" name="listing[other_location]" size="30" type="text" /> 
        <div id="other_location_choices" class="autocomplete">
        </div> 

        <script type="text/javascript"> 
        //<![CDATA[
        new Autocompleter.Local('listing_other_location', 'other_location_choices', ["Turnhout","Tuscaloosa","Zwolle The Netherlands"],{ afterUpdateElement: ListingSignup.show_preview_other_location})
        //]]>
        </script> 
      </div> 
    </div> 
    <div class="contact"> 
      <h2>Finally, how can clients get in touch?</h2> 
      <p> 
        <label for="listing_contact_email">Sales contact email</label> - optional<br /> 
        <small>This is how clients will contact you (example: sales@mydomain.com)</small> 
      </p> 
      <input id="listing_contact_email" name="listing[contact_email]" size="30" type="text" /> 
      <p> 
        <label for="listing_website_url">Website URL</label> - optional<br /> 
        <small>(example: mydomain.com)</small> 
      </p> 
      <input id="listing_website_url" name="listing[website_url]" size="30" type="text" /> 
    </div> 
    <div id='submit_button'> 
      <p><input alt="Save and continue" class="submit_image" onclick="ListingSignup.show_spinner()" src="/images/btn_saveandcontinue.png" type="image" /></p> 
    </div> 
  </form>
</div> 

